00:28:48.400 --> 00:28:51.780
This is the village entrance. Is this where you and Ye Wenjie agreed to meet?

260
00:28:51.780 --> 00:28:52.790
Yeah.

261
00:28:52.790 --> 00:28:55.570
(Qijiatun)
Professor Ye said a villager would come to pick me up,

262
00:28:55.570 --> 00:28:58.620
that I might wait under the big cypress outside the village.

263
00:28:58.620 --> 00:29:00.680
I think it's that one.

264
00:29:03.830 --> 00:29:05.790
It's almost time.

265
00:29:05.790 --> 00:29:07.270
How about you wait here for her?

266
00:29:07.270 --> 00:29:10.820
I'll pay a visit to the village committee to get some information about Shen Yufei's factory.

267
00:29:10.820 --> 00:29:12.370
Alright.

268
00:29:15.830 --> 00:29:17.240
When you see Ye Wenjie,

269
00:29:17.240 --> 00:29:19.540
memorize what she says and tell me when I get back.

270
00:29:19.540 --> 00:29:21.210
I will.

271
00:29:45.690 --> 00:29:47.350
Are you Wang Miao?

272
00:29:47.350 --> 00:29:49.770
You're Wang Miao, right?

273
00:29:49.770 --> 00:29:51.350
I am.

274
00:29:51.350 --> 00:29:54.860
I'm Qi Jianguo. Hop on. Professor Ye sent me here to pick you up.

275
00:29:54.860 --> 00:29:56.810
Hop on. Hop on.

276
00:29:57.620 --> 00:29:59.110
Alright.

277
00:30:00.830 --> 00:30:03.060
Take it easy. Be careful.

278
00:30:07.310 --> 00:30:08.110
Hold on tight.

279
00:30:08.110 --> 00:30:10.460
It's gonna be a bumpy ride.

280
00:30:21.350 --> 00:30:23.350
Does Professor Ye come back often?

281
00:30:23.350 --> 00:30:24.960
No.

282
00:30:24.960 --> 00:30:27.200
But she used to live in our village when she was younger.

283
00:30:27.200 --> 00:30:30.590
She boarded with us. We're very close.

284
00:30:30.590 --> 00:30:32.790
I heard there's a red ginseng factory in your village.

285
00:30:32.790 --> 00:30:34.590
Yes, there is.

286
00:30:34.590 --> 00:30:36.550
The owner's a foreigner.

287
00:30:36.550 --> 00:30:39.480
He rented a large piece of land from us.

288
00:30:39.480 --> 00:30:42.480
He said it'd help us get re-employed.

289
00:30:42.480 --> 00:30:44.070
I think it's a great idea.

290
00:30:44.070 --> 00:30:47.620
Those who don't want to be peasants may work in the factory.

291
00:30:47.620 --> 00:30:50.790
Work? What kind of work?

292
00:30:50.790 --> 00:30:54.960
Cleaning ginseng, digging ginseng, picking out ginseng,

293
00:30:54.960 --> 00:30:57.160
and watching the factory for them.

294
00:30:57.160 --> 00:31:00.160
Does Professor Ye have anything to do with the factory?

295
00:31:00.160 --> 00:31:01.620
I don't think so.

296
00:31:01.620 --> 00:31:02.900
That's a foreigner's factory.

297
00:31:02.900 --> 00:31:04.640
What could she have to do with it?

298
00:31:04.640 --> 00:31:07.110
By the way, there's a flashlight in there.

