Ms. Ye, this is it?

302
00:32:04.070 --> 00:32:05.380
Yeah.

303
00:32:05.380 --> 00:32:08.440
This is Red Coast.

304
00:32:20.030 --> 00:32:25.790
At that time, I thought I'd never be able to leave this place,

